description:
In an effort to "mature" up the site a bit, I was happy to be working with Trent, a big beefy dude from New York.
Trent was eager to do a solo and has done work with one of the major players in the industry.
A hot video as he really likes to show off. And there is even some bonus action at the end.
Enjoy!
title: Trent Alexander - Solo
